{"tid":2500161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友話啲蚊識搭𨋢","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T12:29:06.000Z","uid":311743,"like":14,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"35ffa1d1e1a204b40dabb1f621c646a4727e1b4d","tid":2500161,"uid":311743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"話說我算住喺高層，平時屋企冇咩蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日唔知咩事日日都有蚊飛下飛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我男朋友話啲蚊係搭𨋢上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽到第一時間就喺條街度瘋狂大笑，一諗起隻蚊搭𨋢就覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢覺得我唔信佢 係咁解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟啲蚊真係識搭𨋢 定 佢純粹氹我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a63b00ce57acec588e40e18763bf7457ca5dff","tid":2500161,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"6b7a266f9cac5d1f7da04721da2fe422360768f0","tid":2500161,"uid":63183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"應該真係識搭𨋢，跟住個人行入𨋢"},{"pid":"632fbd54764aefc14432c39f5ebb6ddae58d3f7d","tid":2500161,"uid":286155,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"邊有咁醒<br />\n佢地係行樓梯上黎"},{"pid":"4c48050624b7532dad6c8112f9f2cc9bc3e85f30","tid":2500161,"uid":29947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"632fbd54764aefc14432c39f5ebb6ddae58d3f7d","tid":2500161,"uid":286155,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"邊有咁醒<br />\n佢地係行樓梯上黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"點開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4696c590a985c27f6174848415aae1f8c65c4874","tid":2500161,"uid":3